snippet.title: Synthesia
snippet.description:
We share actionable tutorials about video creation, marketing, and AI.

Synthesia is an AI video creation platform that transforms text into professional videos with customizable avatars—no cameras needed. Fast, cost-effective, and perfect for training, marketing, and education, it’s revolutionizing how businesses and creators communicate.

On Synthesia’s YouTube channel, you’ll master the art of video creation. From basics like converting text to video, to advanced topics like creating custom avatars that look and sound 100% like you!

Beyond tutorials, we share insightful case studies from our research and the AI video industry.

Our mission is simple: to educate and empower you to harness the power of video with AI.
